      • Halfsegment

        public Halfsegment(PointIF p0,
                   PointIF p1,
                   boolean leftDominating)
        Constructor to create a 'Halfsegment' object by passing the endpoints and a flag which indicate the dominating point of this segment
        The passed points will be assigned to the internal leftPoint and rightPoint by the following rule:
        leftPoint = min(p0, p1)
        rightPoint = max(p0, p1)
        Parameters:
        p0 - - first endpoint
        p1 - - second endpoint

      • Halfsegment

        public Halfsegment(double x0,
                   double y0,
                   double x1,
                   double y1,
                   boolean leftDominating)
        Constructor to create a 'Halfsegment' object by passing coordinats of the endpoints and a flag which indicate the dominating point
        Parameters:
        x0 - - x value of first endpoint
        y0 - - y value of first endpoint
        x1 - - x value of second endpoint
        y1 - - x value of second endpoint
        leftDominating - - true, left point is dominating - false, right point is dominating

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(HalfsegmentIF otherHS)
        Compare this 'Halfsegment' object to other ones

        dominating points > left dominating point flages > directions (rotations)
